{"serial": "41028", "department_serial": 38, "code": "BA6009", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Investment", "ch": "投資學"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": "MB5046合班上課"}, "instructor": {"en": ["Huang, Yi-Chieh"], "ch": ["黃依潔"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["5", "6", "7"]}, "loc": {"building": "I1", "room": "508"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 20, "department": {"ch": "企業管理學系", "en": "Department of Business Administration"}, "system": {"ch": "碩士班", "en": "Master Programs"}, "language": {"ch": "英語", "en": "English"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 11, "selected": 0, "remark": {"ch": "MB5046合班上課", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程主要針對碩士班以上之學生設計，著重投資學核心理論介紹、期刊文獻閱讀以及討論。學生可透過此課程獲得投資學之核心與進階知識，以及透過閱讀相關期刊文獻了解其應用，另外也可進一步嘗試從中尋找論文研究方向。", "en": "This course which is mainly designed for graduate students focuses on introducing theory of investments, reading related journal papers, and discussion. Students can obtain core and advanced knowledge of investments. Furthermore, by reading related journal papers, they can understand the applications of these knowledge and try to find their research topics on master thesis."}, "outline": {"ch": "1.核心與進階投資學理論介紹：風險與報酬、多元投資、資本資產定價模型、套利定價理論、效率市場假說、行為財務學以及投資績效衡量。\n2.相關期刊文獻閱讀與討論。", "en": "1.Introductions of core and advanced theory of investment, including: risk and returns, diversification, CAPM, APT, efficient market hypothesis, behavioral finance, and investment performance evaluation.\n2.Reading and discussion of related journal papers."}, "textbook": {"ch": "1. Zvi Bodie, Alan J. Marcus, and Alex Kane, “Essentials of Investments”, 2022 (12e), McGraw Hill Education (華泰文化代理).\n2. Zvi Bodie, Alan J. Marcus, and Alex Kane, “Investments”, 2021 (12e), McGraw Hill Education (華泰文化代理).\n3. 相關期刊文獻。", "en": "1. Zvi Bodie, Alan J. Marcus, and Alex Kane, “Essentials of Investments”, 2022(12e), McGraw Hill Education (Dealer: Hwa-Tai Publishing).\n2. Zvi Bodie, Alan J. Marcus, and Alex Kane, “Investments”, 2021 (12e), McGraw Hill Education (Dealer: Hwa-Tai Publishing).\n3.Selected journal papers."}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "30", "en": "30"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "期中報告：30％;\n期末報告：40％;\n課堂參與: 30％ (討論：20％、出席：10％)。", "en": "Midterm presentation: 30％;\nFinal presentation: 40％;\nClass participation: 30％, including: discussion 20％ and attendance 10％."}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週四 11:00-11:50 (請來信預約)", "en": "Thursday 11:00-11:50 (By appointment)"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "視課程進度需要，安排額外課程討論或報告。", "en": "Additional course discussion or paper presentation would be arranged if needed."}, "domain": {"ch": "財務管理", "en": "財務管理"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "管理知識", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考和解決問題能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "國際觀", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "社會責任", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "溝通能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Management Knowledge", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Critical Thinking and Problem-solving", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Global Perspective", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Social Responsibility", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Communication Skill", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance"]}]}, "assignCriteri